 be an indication of free-free optical depth within an ionized\nwind, a photoevaporating disk, or an accretion flow. It is less likely that\nthis increase is caused by dust emission at 0.7 cm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Sep 2003 17:50:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
